  "text": "Artifact Correction. Ocular artifacts can be corrected for instance using ICA. This is currently possible via a provided MATLAB function that applies ICA functions to the ELAN data file using the freely available EEGLab toolbox [CITATION_1] . In addition, data from bad or missing channels can be reconstructed by interpolation using spline functions.",
